ActBoards of Trade Act
SubjectTaber & District Chamber of Commerce (Alberta) ** Change of Boundaries **
PrecisOrder approving the application by the TABER & DISTRICT CHAMBER OF COMMERCE, in Alberta, to CHANGE THE BOUNDARIES OF ITS DISTRICT from the municipal district of Taber to the Town of Taber and adjoining territory; North to Highway 521 and Highway 875; East to Cypress County and County of Forty Mile boundaries; South to County of Warner boundary; and West to County of Lethbridge boundary.
